    "compareTitle": "Compare plans",
    "faqTitle": "Frequently asked questions",
    "faq": {
      "q1": "Do you provide native English teachers?",
      "a1": "Yes. GeckoTeach includes optional native English teachers who work with your students on our platform. You get both the platform and teaching support — curriculum, classes, and tracking in one place.",
      "q2": "How do I get a custom quote?",
      "a2": "Book a demo and we'll walk you through the platform, discuss your student count and goals, and provide a tailored quote. Pricing depends on seats and whether you add Gecko teachers.",
      "q3": "Can we use only the platform with our own teachers?",
      "a3": "Yes. The Platform Only tier gives you the full GeckoTeach platform — placement tests, classroom management, teacher dashboard, recordings, and analytics — for your own teachers to use.",
      "q4": "Is teacher training included?",
      "a4": "Full Program Partner plans include teacher training and academic reporting. Platform + Teachers and Platform Only can add training as an optional service. Ask during your demo."
    },
